  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42421875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCyRJeynGbmz6Wls6JSVMXdXccFyRQUlmniaEd40wbQ6IRSOCTUabFeBg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"245\" data-imgfileid=\"505175897\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ca792f10&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCyRJeynGbmz6Wls6JSVMXdXccFyRQUlmniaEd40wbQ6IRSOCTUabFeBg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">马斯克在2025最后一天连夜贴脸开大！自建电厂、暴力圈地，直指微软是「微小且软」。另一边，被逼疯的谷歌密谋算力翻千倍。2026决战前夜，AI早已脱离代码，变成一场抢夺电力与地皮的「物理战争」！</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不出意外的，又出意外了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">马斯克在2025年的最后一天也不消停，连夜对微软贴脸开大：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7012089810017271\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1158\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1158\" data-height=\"812\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"394\" data-imgfileid=\"505175912\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c063978c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCaTTiaEVOO2Q3icjQKVFicxpnsvg0xunkYliapWV2iaFtPc2svHQWY9qnicMg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这个「微小且软（Microsoft）」的反面，马斯克要建立一个「宏大且硬（Macrohard）」的AI帝国。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一边，谷歌正密谋着要在5年内将算力拉升1000倍；另一边，马斯克为了给百万块芯片供电，直接在工地旁自己盖起了发电厂。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2026年还没到，硅谷的空气里就已弥漫着浓浓的火药味。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一场关于土地、电力、以及私人恩怨的「物理战争」，正式开启。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">生死时速：谷歌的极限自救</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">谷歌AI基础设施负责人Amin Vahdat甩出一组幻灯片，全场陷入死寂。他的要求只有一句话：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;blockquote&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;editId&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;nickname&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;authorName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;from&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">谷歌必须在未来4-5年内，将计算能力提升1000倍。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5620641562064156\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"717\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"717\" data-height=\"403\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505175913\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6583819d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCVVZqSb7q4icNcxgpF3JgibRQyTodMymZicOoYdrh97f5mKX8DVA7p3vCA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">换算下来，谷歌的基础设施能力，每6个月就要翻一倍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种近乎「自虐」的要求，逼得CEO桑达尔·皮查伊也开始诉苦。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他以谷歌引以为傲的视频生成工具Veo为例，明明效果惊人，却因为算力不足，迟迟不敢在Gemini里向更多用户开放。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种感觉，就像手里握着核武器，却因为交不起电费，只能锁在保险柜里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了打破这个僵局，谷歌开始疯狂抠能效。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们最新推出的第七代芯片Ironwood，硬生生把能效比拉到了第一代的30倍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4336842105263158\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"950\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"950\" data-height=\"412\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"244\" data-imgfileid=\"505175914\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ea33ba4d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCP6YyeJTU0ibA2bXejyLcVB0JomAXJ5yRicawJX2doQ3y7FR0hdgj80Bw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">谷歌的目标很明确。既然外部电力供不上，就要最大程度榨出每一张芯片、每一度电的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在2026这个决战时刻，皮查伊直言：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">因畏手畏脚而「投入不足」的风险，远比「投入过剩」要大得多。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">马斯克的暴力美学：手搓能源帝国</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当谷歌拿着电表钻研算法时，马斯克已经开着推土机，在田纳西州地荒地上玩了一场现实版的「模拟城市」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不同于谷歌对能效的极致克扣，马斯克的逻辑简单粗暴：既然电不够用，我就自己盖发电站；地皮不够大，我就买下整个仓库。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2000\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2000\" data-height=\"1500\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"422\" data-imgfileid=\"505175915\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=433f9c8a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCoW49yyPwdZ6Iwq2sVGPqdexLx29xGSPiaTaA4LDpvhibr2VicroWUhm7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了实现「百万芯片」的宏伟蓝图，马斯克大手一挥，在孟菲斯和密西西比的交界处建了一座发电厂。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随后，又还豪掷千金，买下81万平方英尺的巨型仓库，直接通过合资公司手搓出了一座2GW级别的算力中心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.5985915492957747\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"852\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"852\" data-height=\"1362\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"898\" data-imgfileid=\"505175916\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=92444c80&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCjfQxMEWc0wWAZiaqI6jNa8M1iaNQUGjxTiaxs3q013PNicd85D4GzlOibhA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">密西西比州和孟菲斯州的交界处建设发电厂，这样既提高了获取许可的几率，又减少了远距离电费高昂的问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最疯狂的是，他打算完全不依赖当的电网，而是在工地旁建起了一条属于自己的天然气供能战线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在他眼里，AI竞赛的下半场不是智力问答，而是体力活——不需要优雅的能效曲线，只要那一万亿亿次的算力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">哪怕要把仓库改成发电厂，哪怕要用最短的时间消耗掉整座城市的能源储备，他也在所不惜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种不计成本的疯狂扩张，只为了一个目标：抢在2026年之前，手里握着最庞大、最原始的「算力煤矿」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">顶级商战：名字里的恶趣味</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">马斯克的逻辑很简单，甚至有些孩子气——既然你叫Micro，我就要叫Macro压你一头；你叫soft，我就偏要hard到底。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种贴脸开大在2025年不仅没收敛，反而疯狂升级。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从最初调侃式的Macrohard，到后来充满挑衅的Macroharder，再到他最新认领的第三座大楼名字：MACROHARDRR。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5201822916666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1536\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1536\" data-height=\"799\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"292\" data-imgfileid=\"505175918\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=db23c608&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCfzEWicdlHqPraCnYva2APUqCVcn5KwscEpQmKmlg5bgyZicPM7lRCNyA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">看着满屏的字母「R」，我们隔着屏幕都能感受到马斯克对微软的挑衅：你靠软件起家，我偏要用最硬核的基建，把你打趴下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这背后或许是积压已久的「夺子之恨」。马斯克始终无法释怀OpenAI「背叛」自己，投靠微软。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8700173310225303\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1154\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1154\" data-height=\"1004\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"489\" data-imgfileid=\"505175920\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2c51f5f9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCsicVDu8E6zvfGdrwpSvB7ibG5LmMCRoYACibRgc2NF5IqRX5FZu39xbXQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4413793103448276\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1160\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1160\" data-height=\"512\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"248\" data-imgfileid=\"505175919\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=74a5af28&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCAvsStuJfhdmmvqNXt2qB92LnpibYTeicpTmia4PryF4QlDicv70DhtrBAA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他曾多次出言挑衅：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">既然你们已经成了微软的闭源子公司，那我就亲手建一个「全AI驱动、全硬件支撑」的帝国，在每一个物理维度上，都比你更「巨」、更「硬」。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">两个时代、两种性格正面碰上了——</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">个在云端维持着优雅的平衡，一个在工地上叫嚣着要推翻一切。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">当AI与现实碰撞</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，当马斯克在X上尽情嘲讽时，现实世界却在发出一阵阵痛苦的轰鸣。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这场「宏大且硬」的战争，有重量，也有代价。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了在2026年决战前上线百万芯片，马斯克不等电力审批通过，直接在居民区旁强行插上几十台移动燃气轮机。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1200\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"1200\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"505175922\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=03c14db6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCLYoq2dbRmeV7m4sphMCHYAibR5NibHCl7LgklON5Y8Vtu8QQGrl9rfqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI在数字世界里思考人类的未来，却在现实世界里排出废气和噪声。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在孟菲斯街头，环保活动家和愤怒的邻居正在抗议。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3132183908045977\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1392\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1392\" data-height=\"436\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"176\" data-imgfileid=\"505175923\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9590c9c8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCZCqzI8Pg4T82iasdWyxCcibQCtjfxhazgbhG31I2E8RtNiaK5Z259OHzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">原本平静的生活，正随着发电机组的震动变得支离破碎。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">面对这些反对声，马斯克没有停下推土机，而是玩起了一场跨越州界的「捉迷藏」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了躲避监管，他连夜把基建设备跨州搬运；为了封锁怨言，他筑起了一面巨大的隔音墙。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这画面荒诞至极，却又无比真实：人类最前沿的智慧，正寄居在最笨重、最吵闹、甚至最受人嫌弃的工业怪兽里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人类最前沿的智慧，正寄居在最笨重、最吵闹、甚至最受人嫌弃的工业怪兽里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1536\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1536\" data-height=\"1024\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"505175924\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=642742ed&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCnCJf7LjIMEXNHicrxQfXew4lrUKpLrhsqoeufcBiaUKFPTeHKXCH06ibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2025年5月7日星期三，田纳西州孟菲斯 xAI 数据中心外可以看到燃气轮机。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">无论马斯克如何用「MACROHARDRR」去嘲讽软件的虚无，他都不得不面对一个现实——AI 竞赛的终点，不再是单纯的代码优劣而是如何搞定电网，怎样才能不惊扰民众。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2026年的脚步越来越近。在皮查伊的计算里，那是算力翻千倍的决战时刻；在马斯克的推土机声中，那是「宏大且硬」的帝国元年。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们正在见证一场没有刹车的进化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当AI脱离了实验室的温床，开始在荒地上抢夺电力、在州界线旁筑起高墙、在社交媒体上互相嘲讽，它才真正展示出作为「下一代工业文明」的狰狞与强悍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5622222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1800\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1800\" data-height=\"1012\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505175925\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=08e8d9a6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCricTyXNcHiccKBxd7VVg4ykUSRUpwe7ibHPC4wam0NyrTyEmHXicIfciboA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这场战争最终的胜负，也许已经不重要了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">重要的是，从2026年起，世界将再也没有「纯粹」的互联网公司。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所有的巨头，都必须在土地、电力和震耳欲聋的机械轰鸣中，去置换那张通往未来的入场券。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">硅谷的旧秩序正在崩塌，而新秩序，正刻在那些冒着热气的发电机组上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/ai/2025/11/google-tells-employees-it-must-double-capacity-every-6-months-to-meet-ai-demand/\" target=\"_blank\">https://arstechnica.com/ai/2025/11/google-tells-employees-it-must-double-capacity-every-6-months-to-meet-ai-demand/</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://x.com/SERobinsonJr/status/2006092842569978336?s=20\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/SERobinsonJr/status/2006092842569978336?s=20</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://x.com/elonmusk/status/2006108047609930069\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/elonmusk/status/2006108047609930069</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.theinformation.com/articles/elon-musks-xai-buys-building-third-supersized-data-center?rc=epv9gi\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theinformation.com/articles/elon-musks-xai-buys-building-third-supersized-data-center?rc=epv9gi</a></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\">\n   <br>\n  </p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "AI 竞赛从代码战升级为资源战，马斯克与谷歌分别以“暴力美学”和“极限自救”模式争夺电力与土地，预示着 AI 已成为一场“物理战争”，改变了科技巨头的生存法则。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "AI 竞赛从代码战升级为资源战，马斯克与谷歌分别以“暴力美学”和“极限自救”模式争夺电力与土地，预示着 AI 已成为一场“物理战争”，改变了科技巨头的生存法则。",
  "summary": "本文围绕 2025 年末至 2026 年初，AI 领域巨头之间从软件算法竞争转向对电力、土地等物理资源的争夺这一趋势展开。文章以谷歌和马斯克的 xAI 为例，展现了科技公司对算力需求的极度渴求：谷歌计划五年内将算力提升 1000 倍，通过优化芯片能效应对挑战；马斯克则采取更“暴力”的方式，自建发电厂、购买巨型仓库，以“MACROHARDRR”之名直接与“Microsoft”对垒，讽刺其“微小且软”。这种“物理战争”不仅体现在资源抢夺上，还引发了环境和社会问题，如燃气轮机带来的污染和噪音。文章指出，未来的 AI 竞赛将不再是单纯的代码比拼，而是对基础物理设施的控制权之争，宣告了“纯粹”互联网公司的终结，预示着新工业文明的到来。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 竞争向物理基础设施（电力、土地）的战略转移。",
      "explanation": "随着 AI 大模型发展，算力需求呈指数级增长，传统软件和算法层面的竞争已不足以支撑，企业开始将重心转向实际的能源和数据中心建设。"
    },
    {
      "point": "谷歌与马斯克代表两种不同的应对策略。",
      "explanation": "谷歌通过极致能效优化（如 Ironwood 芯片研发）应对算力需求，力求在现有框架内实现高效率；马斯克则采取更激进的“暴力美学”，通过自建电厂、大规模圈地等方式直接控制底层资源，以确保算力供给。"
    },
    {
      "point": "科技巨头的竞争已超越商业范畴，引发社会和环境问题。",
